Short Description
Coming in many different colors, Thingamakin Elders are rare fully-grown ⁠Thingamakin Juveniles that have managed to miraculously survive long enough to gain human-like sentience and now live alongside us... whether we want these dusty humanoids to or not.
They wear objects as pieces of clothing to represent themselves, alongside seeming to have an innate sense of color theory— as they often pick items that match the color of their dusty forms quite well.

